original_title: Jenny Secoma In: The Blind Spot
overview: Jenny Secoma is an exorcist with not enough jobs, too many bills, and a liver that could use a day off. She’s not feeling too well at the moment. Paranoia and terror hound her at every corner. Sleepless nights, restless days, and the incessant pressure of an unceasing gaze. Something… or someone… is watching her. What could it be?
title: Jenny Secoma In: The Blind Spot
